lyrics:

imageDescription: A magician dressed in a black suit and hat stands in the center of a stage. He is surrounded by a cloud of smoke, and there are several doves flying around him. In one hand he holds a deck of cards, and in the other hand he holds a wand. The magician is looking directly at the viewer with a confident smile on his face.
